attributes.action: STOP WDC housing development in the Gomm Valley
attributes.additional_details:
We need to stop Wycombe District Council from going ahead with the housing development on Gomm Valley.
They are proposing to build 400 homes in this area, with an access from Hammersley Lane between the railway bridge and Robinson rd. They have obviously not driven this route between 8am and 9.30 am when it is at a stand still !!!.
